In components, use theme-based keywords such as `bg-primary`, `text-mutedD, `rounded-lg`, `p-md`.
**Arbitrary-value classes like `w-[123px]` or `text-[#abc]` are strictly forbidden.**

- Use spacing tokens: `p-md`, `gap-2`, `px-3`, `py-2` 
- Use size tokens: `text-sm`, `text-md`, `text-lg`, `text-xl`, `text-2xl` 
- Use radius tokens: `rounded-lg`, `rounded-xl`, `rounded-full` 
- All components must follow the theme system consistently
